12:00.666 --> 12:04.470
I think most of the time I've been asked that question has been from the premise of debate.

12:06.412 --> 12:08.154
But here's the truth about that.

12:09.476 --> 12:10.557
Where did God come from?

12:10.597 --> 12:12.059
He's always been.

12:12.119 --> 12:18.106
Now, that's a true, that's a simple answer, but it's the truth.

12:18.346 --> 12:20.649
He's always, he had no beginning, he had no end.

12:20.669 --> 12:21.810
In fact, he

12:22.210 --> 12:30.081
Through the Lord Jesus Christ, I think is represented well in the order of Melchizedek and the Old Testament.

12:30.101 --> 12:31.083
He had no beginning.

12:31.143 --> 12:32.765
He has no ending.

12:32.965 --> 12:34.247
He's the Alpha Omega.

12:35.128 --> 12:41.177
So there's some things about God that is just not going to be possible to wrap our brains around.

12:41.197 --> 12:44.041
We just don't know, but here's one listed for you tonight.

12:44.061 --> 12:44.842
The other is this.

12:45.483 --> 12:50.610
The mystery of the seven stars and we're in Revelation and this comes up in Revelation 1.20.

12:51.906 --> 13:06.123
The mystery of the seven stars, which thou sawest in my right hand, and the seven golden candlesticks, the seven stars are the seven angels of the seven churches, and the seven candlesticks, which thou sawest are the seven churches.

13:06.704 --> 13:10.048
And we can figure this out pretty much as we study the word.

13:11.129 --> 13:18.738
Now, then there's the mystery of the woman on the beast in Revelation chapter 17 and verse number seven.

13:19.682 --> 13:32.500
And the angel said unto me, wherefore this thou marvel, I will tell thee the mystery of the woman and of the beast that carryeth her, which hath the seven heads and ten horns.

13:33.322 --> 13:36.687
All right, we shall soon get to Revelation 17 in the journey.

13:37.408 --> 13:38.529
Let me give you one more.

13:39.290 --> 13:44.658
The mystery of Israel, Romans chapter 11, verse number 25.

13:45.442 --> 13:52.851
For I would not brethren that you should be ignorant of the mystery of this mystery lest you should be wise in your own concepts.

13:54.293 --> 14:02.263
That blindness in part is happened to Israel until the fullness of the Gentiles be come in.

14:03.044 --> 14:03.385
All right.

14:03.405 --> 14:13.938
