14:14.466 --> 14:17.449
and I have given you the scripture references for these.

14:17.469 --> 14:24.517
Now these mysteries are distinct from the mysteries of God, I believe in our present age.

14:26.800 --> 14:30.104
The mystery and revelation, for example, 10, seven.

