15:28.978 --> 15:31.502
So the question comes from this.

15:34.426 --> 15:42.418
God has allowed, and I emphasize aloud, He has allowed the devil to rule the affairs of men

15:43.362 --> 15:45.525
for a little more than 6,000 years.

15:47.268 --> 15:51.234
Scriptures clearly teach us that the devil is the prince of the power of the air.

15:53.117 --> 16:12.146
Now, do you remember in the story of Job, the devil came to God and said, listen, this great servant of yours, let me paraphrase this a little bit tonight, this great servant of yours, you think he's a big deal God, but I promise you,

16:13.282 --> 16:18.610
You give me the opportunity and I will bring this man to his knees where he will curse you and want to die."

16:21.054 --> 16:26.121
He said, but I can't get to him because you have a hedge about him.

16:28.986 --> 16:37.298
When the discussion was conversed in such a way that the hedge would be moved,

16:39.170 --> 16:46.639
God said, okay, you can do anything to this man that you want to, but you just can't kill him.

16:46.659 --> 16:52.206
I emphasized tonight not on that declaration, but the emphasis is on the hedge.

16:55.630 --> 17:03.199
