17:11.489 --> 17:12.350
You know what I pray for?

17:12.811 --> 17:16.757
I pray that God will constantly keep a headship protection about them.

17:20.722 --> 17:34.642
Whenever we get as a church family and some of our members and folks that are dear to us, whenever we hear that there is a commotion going on in and around their life, and they have to

17:35.074 --> 17:41.364
