19:50.039 --> 19:50.660
You know that.

19:52.141 --> 19:56.946
But again, God has allowed the devil

19:58.850 --> 20:02.294
to officially rule the affairs of men for a little over 6,000 years.

20:02.354 --> 20:07.760
And he has been in the ruling in his operation.

20:08.101 --> 20:17.111
He has completely wrecked, devastated, turned upside down in a most upheaval way.

20:17.572 --> 20:20.054
