20:22.457 --> 20:26.642
And I could give you, we could talk about this forever, but listen carefully.

20:27.170 --> 20:37.963
Here's the thing, we know, even though the devil has ruled the affairs of men for a little over 6,000 years, and in his ruling, he has basically destroyed all of God's creation.

20:38.063 --> 20:38.864
Here's what we know.

20:39.324 --> 20:43.569
We know that God ultimately is more powerful than the devil.

20:45.772 --> 20:47.354
You see, God is omnipotent.

20:48.675 --> 20:49.997
That means he is all power.

20:50.057 --> 20:54.482
We know that Satan's power, listen carefully, is limited

20:55.234 --> 20:59.681
The devil's power is limited by the power of God.

21:01.224 --> 21:02.526
