21:03.748 --> 21:09.898
Satan is mighty, but God is all mighty.

21:11.861 --> 21:17.851
We know that in the end, according to the word of God, that Satan is going to be cast down.

21:18.853 --> 21:21.938
But here is the painful question again, but why?

21:22.882 --> 21:28.109
Why has God allowed him to get by with so much for so long?

21:31.053 --> 21:32.515
I think it's a mystery of God.

21:35.879 --> 21:42.868
And I think the answer really and truly is not for us to know.

21:42.909 --> 21:44.410
That opens up a lot.

21:44.451 --> 21:50.098
Well, I believe, Richard, at the reason, if you go back to this baggy eye, whatever, you can do all that stuff.

21:50.786 --> 21:57.874
But I truly believe this personally by great conviction that this is what I was talking about a moment ago.

21:57.915 --> 21:59.597
This is one of the mysteries of God.

21:59.617 --> 22:01.339
Why has God allowed it?

22:01.779 --> 22:03.962
I don't believe it's for us to know.

22:04.242 --> 22:10.850
I know we have the events in prophecy, but it comes down to this.

22:11.771 --> 22:17.618
Whenever there is a great mystery of God, remember this.

22:18.818 --> 22:24.604
